data.description: Motivated Seller, Bring ALL offers!! All new appliances in 2017. New roof in 2018. New central forced air in 2017 and fully serviced in 2022.. Amazing opportunity to live in the great historic town of canton with about a 30 minute drive to Asheville NC and less than 5 minutes from main street canton. This precious home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Featuring 2 Bedrooms upstairs along with 1 bathroom. Downstairs includes the 3rd bedroom with bathroom with washer and dryer area. Don’t miss out on this great opportunity… just call or text to schedule your showing today!
